{
  "chapter": 46,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十六回\"欢场变屠场\"。方宝玉与熊雄分析孙玉龙\"吴刚斫桂\"与单毅成\"云中电击\"两招的优劣，熊雄警告二人可能联手互换招式。孙玉龙、单毅成到来后以笑里藏刀之态围住宝玉，突然互换兵刃使出对方绝招——孙玉龙以飞龙斧使云中电击攻上路，单毅成以金爪锤使吴刚斫桂攻下路。宝玉早有预料，以巧劲夺斧击锤，令二人相撞落败。战后宝玉向熊雄详解析敌之理：从对方笑声中身法破绽判断出互换招式。王大娘以庆功宴为饵，将众人一一引入后室\"传授武功\"实则偷学各派绝技。小公主调侃熊雄已被掏空本事。王大娘趁众人沉醉，暗落铁闸困住宝玉，欲纵火毁场灭口。她率少女闯入单毅成房中将其刺杀，\"欢场\"顿成\"屠场\"。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "有张缺德的嘴，水里丢了腿；偷上姑娘的楼，云里打破头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "这前面一句，想必是鱼传甲与孙玉龙两人，这两人武功家数虽不同，但攻下三路时之招式却当真各有巧妙。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不错。后面一句话，便说的是'天上飞花'冷冰鱼和这'半天云'单毅成了。冷冰鱼虽然凶，但单毅成那一招'云中电击'，可也不是好玩的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "若论招式之凌厉霸道，'云中电击'只怕还在'天上飞花'之上。只是此招也就失之于霸气太重，是以灵巧不足。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "'吴刚斫桂'和'云中电击'这两招自然各有缺点，否则他俩也就不会败在方兄你的手里了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "吴刚斫桂却是灵巧有余，霸气不足，这只怕便是因为孙玉龙身躯过于瘦小。但话说回来，他若非身躯瘦小，也使不出这样的招式了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "但若是两人联手，同时使出这两招来，一个攻上，一个攻下，这又当如何？方兄你可曾想到此着？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "他两人若是联手同时使出这两招来，倒当真叫人难以应付。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "这就是了，是以方兄千万大意不得。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "说曹操，曹操就到，那两个小子果然已来了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_yi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "单毅成",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "熊老大，你说完了么？让咱们和方大侠聊聊如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方兄可要我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "无妨，熊兄只管走吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_shan_yi_cheng",
      "text": "小心些，莫要自己搬砖砸自己的脚，还是省省事吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_long",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉龙",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "月余不见，方大侠风采越发神俊了。小弟闻得方大侠在泰山上威风八面，着实也欢喜得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_yi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "单毅成",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "只恨咱们这两块不成材的废料竟被人关了起来，没有赶上泰山的热闹，也没能瞧见方大侠的威风。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_long",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_yi_cheng",
      "text": "纵未瞧见，也能想象得到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_yi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "单毅成",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "所以咱们两人便忍不住前来向方大侠道喜。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_long",
      "text": "两位此刻便是特地赶来捧小弟的么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_long",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉龙",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "哪里的话，在下……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_sun_yu_long",
      "text": "两位若是将小弟捧得高高的，再摔下来，小弟可生受不起。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_yi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "单毅成",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方大侠说笑了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说说笑话，本是好的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_yu_long",
      "speaker_name": "孙玉龙",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "是极是极，方大侠说得好！说得好……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_yun",
      "speaker_name": "吕云",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_lv_yun",
      "text": "以方宝玉此刻所摆的架势，左面下部空虚，绝难挡得住孙玉龙的一招'吴刚斫桂'，右面却是上面大露空门，更难招架单毅成的那招'云中电击'。他……他……他怎会做出这样的傻事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "到现在为止，我还未见过方宝玉做出任何一样傻事来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "但……但现在……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪奇怪……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "你如今总该知道他不做傻事了吧！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方兄，方大侠，我如今才知道你武功实比我想象中还高出十倍！我虽然知道你必能将他两人击败，却委实未想到你胜得如此轻松。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "只不过是看来轻松而已，在当时我出手只要差错一分，慢了一分，如今躺下的就该是我了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "其实这还得感激熊兄。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "感激我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "若非熊兄先就告诉我他两人已曾互相研究武功许久，小弟方才便不会以那种身形架势迎敌了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方兄你方才那身形架势又有何巧妙？在下委实更不懂了。在下方才本还在为方兄担心。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "方才我左掌若非在肩头以上，他飞斧击下时，我便赶不及抢得他斧柄，那时我便只有左纵或者后退。我若左纵，虽可避过金爪锤，但右肩势必要伤在飞龙斧下；我若后退，膝头便要被金爪锤打碎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "是以这半分时间之差，便已将胜负之势完全扭转，方才我的生死之别也有如在刀口边缘。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "如此说来，你莫非早已猜出孙玉龙击出的一招必非'吴刚斫桂'，而是'云中电击'么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "方才我听了你的话，就已想到两人既在那黑牢中商议了那么久，便决不会只是各出杀着，联手而攻，只因这两人俱是心机繁复之辈，他们既已商量了那么久，商量的结果便决不会如此简单。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不错……此点我方才怎会想不到？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "他两人此回再来与我较量，出手自然必定要令我大出意料，才能取胜，是以那时我便已想到，他两人极有可能互换招式击出。但在两人还未到我面前之时，我实也不敢完全确定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你如不能确定，又怎会……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "但等到两人在我面前站稳时，我便已确定了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "唉！我还是不懂。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "那时他两人俱在放声大笑，那单毅成笑时肩头动也不动，而孙玉龙却笑得连身子都动了起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "这又与两人出手有何关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "笑时身子摇动，自是下盘不固，就表示他真气已提起。他若要攻我下路，又怎会将气提起？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不错，要使那一招'吴刚斫桂'，下盘必须稳如磐石，下盘既不稳，自不会再使'吴刚斫桂'的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "两人联手，孙玉龙既不攻我下路，单毅成攻的便必定是我下路，是以我立刻便判定他两人必定要互换招式击出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "这道理其实也简单得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "道理虽简单，但你若不说破，我一辈子也想不通，更何况在当时那种四面危机的情况之中。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位都请进来吧，容贱妾备酒，为方大侠庆功。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "熊大侠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "有何见教？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "这地方熊大侠想必是常常来的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "不常来……不常来……只来过四次。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "四次？……嗯！确实不多，但只怕已足够让熊大侠将掏心窝的本事都奉献出来了，也就难怪王大娘不再问你要。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "你真会打岔。你的武功别人已都学会了，这次只怕就要请你在外面坐坐了。眼瞧着别人一个个都做了人幕之宾，你心里怎样？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "熊雄",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我……这……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "没有这样的事。王大娘虽然不是大方的人，但对熊大侠这样的老朋友，还不致如此小气。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_xiong_xiong",
      "text": "鬼丫头，你和熊大侠也不是陌生人了，怎的只知道在这里干坐着，还不快陪熊大侠进去？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "是呀！你只管走吧，还害的什么臊？这又不是什么丢人的事。方少侠还有我陪着，你就放心走吧！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我本当方少侠知道我做的是这种事后必定会勃然大怒，甚至放火烧了我的房子，哪知方少侠却若无其事。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "在下虽非小人，却也非道貌岸然的老夫子。缠头买笑，四海不禁，既是两厢情愿，我又何苦来煞风景。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "对！这才是真英雄的本色。方少侠你若非大英雄，也不会对孙玉龙和单毅成两人如此客气了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "他两人可受了伤么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "伤是没有伤，只不过头顶上多了个大疙瘩。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "亏得他们还有脸呆在这里。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "这你倒错怪他们了，全是我死拖活拉，才将他们拉住的。他两人非但不好意思见方少侠，别的人也不好意思见了，过一阵子只怕还是要悄悄溜了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 411
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "你呀！一心只想偷别人的本事！他两人既已将本事留下了，就算现在走，你也不会拉了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你倒真会猜我的心事，我……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "这些年来，王大娘你所得自然已不少了，却不知大娘你将各门各派的绝艺集于一身，究竟有何打算？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "唷！方少侠这话可问得太厉害了，我哪敢有什么打算。我自从在黄鹤楼受了那次教训后，难道还敢在江湖中兴风作浪不成？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我只不过想让这些女孩子多学些本事。她们都是孤女，都可怜得很，多学些本事，将来就可不再受人欺负，至于我……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我这老残废，已是半死的人了，什么打算也没有了，只是过一天算一天，等着进棺材了事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我说的可是真话，方少侠难道不信？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "但愿果真如此，否则……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方大侠你只管放心，江湖中有方少侠这样的人物在，我若还想动什么坏心思，我可真是瞎了眼了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "不知大娘可否将万老夫人请出来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "她呀！嘿！早已睡得人事不知了，方少侠你就可怜她又老又胖，让她多睡一会儿吧。其实方少侠你也真该歇歇了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "小公主",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "不管她怎样，我好歹可要去歇歇了。王大娘，你的床可得让给我，别的床……别的床太脏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你这小妮子，你懂得什么？丫头们，扶这位千金公主到我床上去……方少侠，你呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "我还有个义弟，在……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方少侠，你也未免太小瞧我了，这种事我还会要方少侠操心吗？你瞧，李名生不是走了许久了么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我知道你那义弟老实得很，生怕我这些鬼丫头逗他，所以就叫李名生拿了肉、提了酒，陪他在那儿喝酒聊天了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "宝玉",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "大娘当真是想得周到。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "人的身子，究竟不是铁打的，方少侠你只管去好生歇一阵子，到了午时，我会去唤醒你的。就算方少侠有要紧的事，也不在乎这半日。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "铁闸落下了么？可曾惊动了他？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "铁闸刚上过油，半点声音也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "你和小七去将那十四口黑箱子全都提到车上，小三和小九去套马，然后你们四个便将火种预备好。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "还有什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "但咱们这么就将这地方毁了，不太可惜么？那姓方的又没对咱们怎样，咱们又何必如此？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "你懂得什么？舍不了孩子打不了狼，要想成大事，还在乎这几间破房子……哼！姓方的一来，我就知道咱们在这里呆不下去了。你听他说的那几句话，笑里藏刀，有多厉害。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 511
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "他再厉害，可也没你老人家厉害。你老人家只不过烧了几间房子，他可要将小命烧死在这里。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "你知道就好……姓方的一死，中土武林中还有谁是咱们娘儿几个的对手？你赶紧去吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们从谁开始？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "我瞧那破锣嗓子最不顺眼，就从他开始好么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": "char_shao_nv",
      "text": "好，就是……他在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "少女",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "他在二姐屋里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "王大娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们走……丫头们，你们且瞧瞧大娘的手段，这些时咱们受那些臭男人的气，可不是白受的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_yi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "单毅成",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "大娘你何苦……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_yi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "单毅成",
      "listener": "char_wang_da_niang",
      "text": "你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 46,
      "line_start": 557,
      "line_end": 557
    }
  ],
